The '''''Province of Cape of Good Hope Official Gazette''''' was the [[government gazette]] of the [[Cape Province|Province of the Cape of Good Hope]]. 

It was published in [[Cape Town]] from June 1910 and<ref>[http://www.crl.edu/collections/topics/official-gazettes/search?titleID=t555&pc=1 SOUTH AFRICA. CAPE PROVINCE (PROVINCE)] CRL Foreign Official Gazette Database, 2014. Retrieved 14 May 2014. [https://www.webcitation.org/6PYzu0Xxo Archived here.]</ref> replaced the ''[[Cape of Good Hope Government Gazette]]'' (1826-1910) when [[Cape Colony]] became a Province.

